Before working, read `.agents/state.md`.

After meaningful work, update `.agents/state.md` and replace the single `Latest Handoff` entry. Keep the file concise.

If `scripts/validate-agent-state.ps1` exists, run:

```powershell
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File scripts\validate-agent-state.ps1
```
